Interface Notifier

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Reader<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNotifier, AbstractProcessor, AbstractReader, AbstractStreamReader, AbstractXmiStreamReader, DefaultMapperReader, EcoreMapper, NoopProcessor, XmiStreamReader, XPathResolver

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public interface Notifier
    An object that notifies registered Handlers of events during an I/O process.
    See Also:
    Handler
